div1.p: IN THE UNITED STATES DISTRICT COURT FOR THE WESTERN DIS- TRICT OF WASHINGTON, NORTHERN DIVISION
IN THE MATTER OF CELIA BERG O'NEILL On Habeas Corpus

It appearing to the Court that the return day on the Order to show cause in the above entitled matter comes on February 24th.1915, and that the Judges of this District will be otherwise engaged in the performance of their duties,
IT IS NOW THEREFORE ORDERED that the hearing on the return day in the above entitled matter be, and the same is hereby continued to and including March 2nd.1915, at 10 a.m.
Dated this 23rd. day of February, A.D., 1915.
